Starting out in any industry can feel intimidating, especially when you don’t have the connections.  to guide you. But here’s @carolagmakeup’s word of advice: never let obstacles hold you back! 

On @ittakesavillagepod, join me for an incredible conversation with Hollywood makeup artist Carola Gonzalez. We talk about her journey from Puerto Rico to Hollywood, the invaluable lessons she learned in starting her own entrepreneurial journey, and other inspiring topics like...

*Starting out in the industry with no connections
*Achieving success and working with some of the biggest names in Hollywood
*The realities of being a makeup artist
*Understanding the business side of the industry
*The art of building and maintaining the right clientele and agent
*Cultivating professional relationships
*The importance of taking time off to recharge creatively
*The transformative power of manifestation
*And many more.

Tune in TODAY on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, YouTube* and wherever you get your podcasts.

#podcastshow #createyourlife #makeupartist #entrepreneurmindset #creativeentrepreneur
